Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.14,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}哼哼喘着粗气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:41.22,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}沿着走廊一阵风跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:45.35,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}今晚是你最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:48.40,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}你想吃的就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:49.48,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1}就是这个没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:53.57,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}加上你就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.99,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}美食和大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.99,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是个围裙男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:06.67,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}围裙男孩 在厨房放连招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.13,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是个围裙男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:14.72,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,0)}围裙男孩 你的笑容是绝品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.09,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我们家团团圆圆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.38,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}笑声满满
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:18.51,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}客厅活像乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:20.55,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}流着口水 洗好小手
